            </button></a>
        </section>
        
        <section id="credits">
            <h2>Site credits</h2>
            <p>
                Made with &#128154; by <strong>Francesco Peluso</strong><br><br>

                Linguaggi di programmazione front-end: <strong>HTML, EJS, JavaScript, CSS</strong><br>
